--------------------------------------------------------------------------
NAME CHANGING
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
The name changing of players or wizards is not allowed.  If you do it
for one person, you are going to have to do it for everyone who asks,
otherwise hard feeling will result.  Since no one wants to cater to
every name chage whim of the players, name changing in any form except
starting a new character under the new name and rm'ing the old charcter
will not be allowed.
